      "span_text": "For example, research has examined how features of residential neighborhoods (eg, built environment, economic opportunity or deprivation) are associated with the health status of neighborhood inhabitants,  but there are considerable challenges in determining whether these associations are causal and, if so, the strength of the causal association."
